sklearn.neighbors.tests.test_neighbors_pipeline module¶

This is testing the equivalence between some estimators with internal nearest neighbors computations, and the corresponding pipeline versions with KNeighborsTransformer or RadiusNeighborsTransformer to precompute the neighbors.
